    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has had 5-6 min, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and<strong> chopped</strong> <strong>pak choi bases </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 1-2 min until softened</p>",
