    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in a bowl with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>hoisin stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
