    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>hoisin stir-fry sauce</strong>,<strong> pak choi green tops</strong>, <strong>drained noodles </strong>and<strong> drained sweetcorn </strong>to the pan with the chicken, season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for a further 1-2 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>speedy hoisin chicken breast noodle stir-fry</strong></p>",
